The paper primarily analyzes AlphaStar through the lens of evolutionary computation (EC), which suggests that cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. Additionally, AlphaStar draws on many areas of AI research, including deep learning (cs.LG), reinforcement learning (cs.AI), game theory (cs.GT), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these sub-categories are also likely.
